            {
               "text": "### The Grid\n\nBelow, we present a version of the grid that performs multiplication using Mesoamerican grids. In the value fields, you can enter any number between 0 and 999. After entering the values, click on the equal sign ( <i class=\"fa-solid fa-equals\"></i> ) to view the result.\n\nRegarding the results, when the product of the multiplication in the grid is greater than 19, instead of showing the number directly, the operation being performed will be indicated. To view the final result displayed in the calculation area, you need to click on the advance (<i class=\"fa-solid fa-arrow-right\" style=\"color:#0f0; font-size: 1.2em;\"></i>) button. At that point, the simplification steps explained by Ruy D. Díaz and applied in the previous text (<htcite0>; <htcite1>) will be shown:",
               "source": [
                  {
                     "type": 1,
                     "uuid": "9e7d0cea-d968-4bd5-886e-bc08c824e7ca",
                     "text": "Díaz, Ruy D.",
                     "page": "",
                     "date_time": {
