      {
         "id": "SECTION_conclusion",
         "text": [
            {
               "text": "### Conclusion\n\nThis text brings together different multiplication tools developed by the Indigenous peoples of the American continent (*Abya Yala*). Although no manual has been found explaining how they were used, thanks to the work of various researchers mentioned throughout the text, today we can recreate and apply them to facilitate both learning and the execution of calculations.",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "markdown",
               "PostMention": ""
            }
         ]
